            <ns0:div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <ns0:p>Thalpon, farewell, worthy and blameless Thalpon! Here I lie, having died aged six, a child of swift fate.</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
            <ns0:div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="#Ferrua">
                <ns0:p>Talpone, addio, buono ed irreprensibile Talpone! Qui giaccio, e morto a sei anni, bambine di celere fato.</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
            <ns0:div type="commentary">
                <ns0:p>The name Thalpon is not otherwise attested.</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
